name: Etta_(smuggler)
content:
Etta was a Human male smuggler who operated on Lok, a considerable distance east of Nym's Stronghold during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Etta was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Etta was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
